Layout Uploader:

Generate Template Skeleton
Upload Template
	- Upload .zip with assets in it 
		index.html
		appropriate files (js/css/image assets)

Add user fields to the equation
	Template Name
	Bundle Name
	Author
	Description
	Icon (can choose from list)
	Device type (mixed, desktop, tablet, mobile)
	Portal target (css selector)

Process the template
	- Break up the template client side
		- HEAD information broken up and placed in one file.
		- Body template broken out and placed in another file.

Register the template
